metadata.test_query:
with cur as (
        
        with baseline as (
            select lower(column_name) as column_name, data_type
            from d_harato_db.elementary."test_60fb698bb7_elementary_source_schema_changes_from_baseline_notion_work_log_true__true__schema_baseline__tmp_20250403123005501664"
        )

        select
            columns_snapshot.full_table_name,
            lower(columns_snapshot.column_name) as column_name,
            columns_snapshot.data_type,
            (baseline.column_name IS NULL) as is_new,
            
    cast ('2025-04-03 12:30:07' as timestamp)
 as detected_at
        from (

    

    with table_info as (
        select
            cast('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG' as varchar) as full_table_name,
            cast('d_harato_db' as varchar) as database_name,
            cast('notion' as varchar) as schema_name,
            cast('work_log' as varchar) as table_name,
            
    cast ('2025-04-03 12:30:07' as timestamp)
 as detected_at
    ),

    columns_info as (
        select
            full_table_name,
            database_name,
            schema_name,
            table_name,
            column_name,
            data_type,
            detected_at
        from table_info
        cross join
            (
                
                    select
                        cast('FETCHED_AT' as varchar) as column_name,
                        cast('TIMESTAMP_LTZ' as varchar) as data_type
                    
                        union all
                    
                
                    select
                        cast('FETCHED_DT' as varchar) as column_name,
                        cast('DATE' as varchar) as data_type
                    
                        union all
                    
                
                    select
                        cast('CONTEXTS' as varchar) as column_name,
                        cast('VARIANT' as varchar) as data_type
                    
                
            ) rt
    ),

    columns_snapshot as (
        select
            full_table_name,
            database_name,
            schema_name,
            table_name,
            column_name,
            data_type,
            detected_at,
            case when
                    upper(database_name || '.' || schema_name || '.' || table_name || '.' || column_name) not in (
        select full_column_name from "D_HARATO_DB"."ELEMENTARY"."SCHEMA_COLUMNS_SNAPSHOT"
        where detected_at = (select max(detected_at) from "D_HARATO_DB"."ELEMENTARY"."SCHEMA_COLUMNS_SNAPSHOT" where lower(full_table_name) = lower('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG'))
        and lower(full_table_name) = lower('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG')
    )
                    and full_table_name in (
        select distinct full_table_name from "D_HARATO_DB"."ELEMENTARY"."SCHEMA_COLUMNS_SNAPSHOT"
        where detected_at = (select max(detected_at) from "D_HARATO_DB"."ELEMENTARY"."SCHEMA_COLUMNS_SNAPSHOT" where lower(full_table_name) = lower('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG'))
        and lower(full_table_name) = lower('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG')
    )
                then true
                else false
            end as is_new
        from columns_info
    ),

    columns_snapshot_with_id as (
        select
            
  

  md5(cast(coalesce(cast(full_table_name as varchar), '') || '-' || coalesce(cast(column_name as varchar), '') || '-' || coalesce(cast(data_type as varchar), '') as TEXT))
 as column_state_id,
            upper(database_name || '.' || schema_name || '.' || table_name || '.' || column_name) as full_column_name,
            full_table_name,
            column_name,
            data_type,
            is_new,
            detected_at
        from columns_snapshot
        group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7
    )

    select
        cast(column_state_id as varchar) as column_state_id,
        cast(full_column_name as varchar) as full_column_name,
        cast(full_table_name as varchar) as full_table_name,
        cast(column_name as varchar) as column_name,
        cast(data_type as varchar) as data_type,
        cast(is_new as boolean) as is_new,
        cast(detected_at as timestamp) as detected_at
    from columns_snapshot_with_id) columns_snapshot
        left join baseline on (
            lower(columns_snapshot.column_name) = lower(baseline.column_name)
        )
        where lower(columns_snapshot.full_table_name) = lower('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG')
    
    ),

    pre as (
        
        select
            cast('D_HARATO_DB.NOTION.WORK_LOG' as varchar) as full_table_name,
            column_name,
            data_type,
            
    cast ('2025-04-03 12:30:07' as timestamp)
 as detected_at
        from d_harato_db.elementary."test_60fb698bb7_elementary_source_schema_changes_from_baseline_notion_work_log_true__true__schema_baseline__tmp_20250403123005501664"
    
    ),

    type_changes as (

        
        select
            cur.full_table_name,
            'type_changed' as change,
            cur.column_name,
            cur.data_type as data_type,
            pre.data_type as pre_data_type,
            pre.detected_at
        from cur inner join pre
            on (lower(cur.full_table_name) = lower(pre.full_table_name) and lower(cur.column_name) = lower(pre.column_name))
        where pre.data_type IS NOT NULL AND lower(cur.data_type) != lower(pre.data_type)

    ),

    
    columns_added as (

        
        select
            full_table_name,
            'column_added' as change,
            column_name,
            data_type,
            
    cast(null as varchar)
 as pre_data_type,
            detected_at as detected_at
        from cur
        where is_new = true

    ),
    

    columns_removed as (

        
        select
            pre.full_table_name,
            'column_removed' as change,
            pre.column_name as column_name,
            
    cast(null as varchar)
 as data_type,
            pre.data_type as pre_data_type,
            pre.detected_at as detected_at
        from pre left join cur
            on (lower(cur.full_table_name) = lower(pre.full_table_name) and lower(cur.column_name) = lower(pre.column_name))
        where cur.full_table_name is null and cur.column_name is null

    ),

    columns_removed_filter_deleted_tables as (

        
        select
            removed.full_table_name,
            removed.change,
            removed.column_name,
            removed.data_type,
            removed.pre_data_type,
            removed.detected_at
        from columns_removed as removed join cur
            on (lower(removed.full_table_name) = lower(cur.full_table_name))

    ),

    all_column_changes as (

        
        select * from type_changes
        union all
        select * from columns_removed_filter_deleted_tables
        
        union all
        select * from columns_added
        
    ),

    column_changes_test_results as (

        
        select
            
  

  md5(cast(coalesce(cast(full_table_name as varchar), '') || '-' || coalesce(cast(column_name as varchar), '') || '-' || coalesce(cast(change as varchar), '') || '-' || coalesce(cast(detected_at as varchar), '') as TEXT))
 as data_issue_id,
            
    cast ('2025-04-03 12:30:07' as timestamp)
 as detected_at,
            
    trim(split(full_table_name,'.')[0],'"') as database_name

,
            
    trim(split(full_table_name,'.')[1],'"') as schema_name

,
            
    trim(split(full_table_name,'.')[2],'"') as table_name

,
            column_name,
            'schema_change' as test_type,
            change as test_sub_type,
            case
                when change = 'column_added'
                    then 'The column "' || column_name || '" was added'
                when change= 'column_removed'
                    then 'The column "' || column_name || '" was removed'
                when change= 'type_changed'
                    then 'The type of "' || column_name || '" was changed from ' || pre_data_type || ' to ' || data_type
                else NULL
            end as test_results_description
        from all_column_changes
        group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9

    )

        
    select 
  

  md5(cast(coalesce(cast(data_issue_id as varchar), '') || '-' || coalesce(cast(cast('4d7a560d-661a-4b53-9e52-761334753646.test.my_new_project.elementary_source_schema_changes_from_baseline_notion_work_log_True__True.60fb698bb7' as varchar) as varchar), '') as TEXT))
 as id,
        cast('4d7a560d-661a-4b53-9e52-761334753646.test.my_new_project.elementary_source_schema_changes_from_baseline_notion_work_log_True__True.60fb698bb7' as varchar) as test_execution_id,
        cast('test.my_new_project.elementary_source_schema_changes_from_baseline_notion_work_log_True__True.60fb698bb7' as varchar) as test_unique_id,
        *
    from column_changes_test_results

model_runs.name: notion_mart
model_runs.compiled_code:
with
    latest_fetch as (
        select max(fetched_at) as fetched_at from d_harato_db.notion.flatten_source
    )

select *
from d_harato_db.notion.flatten_source
where fetched_at = (select max(fetched_at) from latest_fetch)
order by end_time desc

model_runs.name: flatten_source
model_runs.compiled_code:
with source_data as (select * from d_harato_db.notion.work_log)
select
    fetched_at,
    context.value:id::string as page_id,  -- notionページのid
    context.value:properties."Duration(h)".formula.number::number(38, 1)
    * 60 as duration_minutes,  -- 作業時間
    context.value:properties.status.status.name::string as status,  -- ステータス
    case
        when array_size(context.value:properties."Project Tag".multi_select) > 0
        then context.value:properties."Project Tag".multi_select[0].name::string
        else null
    end as project_tag,  -- プロジェクトタグ
    coalesce(
        context.value:properties."Work Tag".select.name::string, '未設定'
    ) as work_tag,  -- 作業タグ (NULL の場合 '未設定')
    context.value:properties."Start Time".date.start::timestamp_tz as start_time,  -- 開始時間
    context.value:properties."End Time".date.start::timestamp_tz as end_time,  -- 終了時間
    context.value:properties."締切".date.start::date as due_date,  -- 締切
    context.value:url::string as notion_url,  -- notionのページurl
    context.value:created_time::timestamp_tz as created_time,  -- 作成日時
    context.value:last_edited_time::timestamp_tz as last_edited_time  -- 最終編集日時
from source_data, lateral flatten(input => contexts:results) context

model_runs.name: sample_pos_data
model_runs.compiled_code:
WITH base AS (
  SELECT
    -- 購入日時（2025年3月2日から4月1日まで）
    DATEADD(
      minute,
      UNIFORM(0, 43200, RANDOM()),
      '2025-03-02'
    )::TIMESTAMP_LTZ AS purchase_datetime,

    ARRAY_CONSTRUCT(
      'コーヒー', '紅茶', 'サンドイッチ', 'おにぎり', '弁当',
      'サラダ', 'スナック', '飲料水', '菓子パン', 'カップラーメン'
    )[UNIFORM(0, 9, RANDOM())] AS item,

    UNIFORM(100, 1000, RANDOM()) AS price,
    'customer_' || UNIFORM(1, 1000, RANDOM()) AS customer_id,
    ARRAY_CONSTRUCT('東京店', '大阪店', '名古屋店', '福岡店', '札幌店')[UNIFORM(0, 4, RANDOM())] AS store_name,
    'SAMPLE_COLUMNS' as sample_columns
  FROM TABLE(GENERATOR(ROWCOUNT => 10000000))
)

SELECT
  *,
  DATEADD(minute, UNIFORM(1, 720, RANDOM()), purchase_datetime)::TIMESTAMP_LTZ AS loaded_datetime
FROM base

model_runs.name: sample_pos_data_summary
model_runs.compiled_code:
SELECT
  store_name,
  customer_id,
  DATE_TRUNC('day', purchase_datetime) AS purchase_date,
  COUNT(*) AS total_items,
  SUM(price) AS total_amount
FROM d_harato_db.test_elementary.sample_pos_data
GROUP BY store_name, customer_id, DATE_TRUNC('day', purchase_datetime)
